{"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"detectionRate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt","preciseIdentifier":"s:Su","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"detectionRate","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(py)detectionRate","roleHeading":"Instance Property","symbolKind":"property","title":"detectionRate"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/detectionRate","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objc"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"dynamic"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"detectionRate"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Su","text":"UInt"},{"kind":"text","text":" { "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"get"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"set"},{"kind":"text","text":" }"}]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The rate of detections\/recognitions per second in normal performance mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Defaults to 20, meaning that 20 frames per second are detected\/recognized, equally distributed over one second."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When the video frame rate is 30, 10 frames will be skipped and 20 frames will be detected\/recognized."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Note: if you set the detection rate greater to or equal to the video frame rate, no frames will be skipped,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the actual detection rate is limited by the video frame rate."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/detectionrate"]},{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/detectionrate"]}],"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol","title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"symbol"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/detectionRate":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/detectionrate","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/detectionRate","title":"detectionRate","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"detectionRate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Su"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"detectionRate","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The rate of detections\/recognitions per second in normal performance mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Defaults to 20, meaning that 20 frames per second are detected\/recognized, equally distributed over one second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"When the video frame rate is 30, 10 frames will be skipped and 20 frames will be detected\/recognized.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Note: if you set the detection rate greater to or equal to the video frame rate, no frames will be skipped,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the actual detection rate is limited by the video frame rate.","type":"text"}]},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk","type":"topic","title":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Version: 8.0.4","type":"text"}]}},"variantOverrides":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"patch":[{"path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage","value":"occ","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/metadata\/roleHeading","value":"Instance Property","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/metadata\/title","value":"detectionRate","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/metadata\/symbolKind","value":"property","op":"replace"},{"path":"\/metadata\/fragments","value":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"detectionRate"}],"op":"replace"},{"op":"add","path":"\/topicSections","value":null},{"op":"add","path":"\/relationshipsSections","value":null},{"op":"add","path":"\/seeAlsoSections","value":null},{"op":"replace","path":"\/primaryContentSections\/0","value":{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSUInteger","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSUInteger"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"detectionRate"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"}},{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1documentation~1ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK~1SBSDKBaseScannerEnergy